    "Iteration 1 for generating SDoH sentences involved prompting the 538 synthetic sentences to be manually validated to evaluate ChatGPT, which cannot be used with protected health information.",
    "Of these, after human review only 480 were found to have any SDoH mention, and 289 to have an adverse SDoH mention (Table 5).",
    "For all synthetic data generation methods, no real patient data were used in prompt development or fine-tuning.",
    "The radiotherapy corpus was split into a 60%/20%/20% distribution for training, development, and testing respectively.",
    "The entire immunotherapy and MIMIC-III corpora were held-out for out-ofdomain tests and were not used during model development."
